name: You don't always have to be strong
description:
It's easy to fall into the trap of always having to be the strong one. It's ok to admit you're struggling and it's ok to ask for help.

Mixed media art journal pages made in an upcycled modular planner, 9" x 7", 5448 x 4150 px, acrylic paint, vintage/found paper, gelatos, ink.
